#

Classic Ham and Cheese Crepes

25 min
$10
300 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

glutendairyegg

Dietary Tags:

high proteinlow carb

Cuisine:

French

Course:

Main

Tags:

easysavorybreakfastbrunch

Description

Delicate crepes filled with savory ham and melted cheese, perfect for a quick and satisfying meal!

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 1 cup
  • milk: 1 cup
  • eggs: 2
  • ham: 1 cup, diced
  • cheese (swiss or gruyère): 1 cup, shredded
  • butter: 2 tbsp
  • salt: 1/2 tsp
  • black pepper: to taste
  • parsley (optional): for garnish
